        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "thatched-roof gate (used as the entrance to a garden, esp. of a tea ceremony house)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "茶室へ続く庭園には、趣のある茅門が静かに佇んでいた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "茅門をくぐると、そこは日常から切り離された別世界のように感じられた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「この茅門、なんだか歴史を感じさせるね。」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "茅門の向こうには、手入れの行き届いた日本庭園が広がっていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "ちょっと好いだろう」　お延は網代組の竹垣の中程にあるその茅門を支えている釿なぐりの柱と丸太の桁を見較べた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "明暗",
                "author": "夏目漱石",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "my home",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
